## Project Structure
- /src/services/ - Business logic and API integrations
- /src/screens/ - React Native screens
- /src/components/ - Reusable UI components
- /src/hooks/ - Custom React hooks
- /src/types/ - TypeScript type definitions
- /src/theme/ - Colors and styling constants
- /supabase/ - Supabase local config and migrations

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow React Native best practices
- Use functional components with hooks
- Keep services separated from UI logic

## Environment Variables
- SUPABASE_URL - Supabase project URL
- SUPABASE_ANON_KEY - Supabase anonymous key
- STRAVA_CLIENT_ID - Strava OAuth client ID
- STRAVA_CLIENT_SECRET - Strava OAuth client secret



